OL,3,C'Enough is enough': Marcus Rashford
OL,4,Ccondemns racist abuse
OL,6,FMarcus Rashford has replied to social
OL,7,Fmedia post saying "enough is enough",
OL,8,Fcalling for an end to the abuse the
OL,9,FManchester United forward has been
OL,10,Freceiving "for months".
OL,12,FThe England and United player
OL,13,Fresponded to the post from the account
OL,14,Fon X, UtdParadigm, which said: "The
OL,15,Fway Marcus Rashford is being treated
OL,16,Fis absolutely disgusting. It's cruel.
OL,17,FIt's abuse".
OL,19,FRashford responded: "I appreciate your
OL,20,Fsupport! It is abuse and has been for
OL,21,Fmonths. Enough is enough".
