OL,6,FHe pleaded guilty to sending an
OL,7,Foffensive/abusive message by a public
OL,8,Fcommunication network at Warrington
OL,9,FMagistrates' Court and was sentenced
OL,10,Fto 14 weeks in prison suspended for 18
OL,11,Fmonths.
OL,13,FIn 2022, Justin Lee Price, 19, was
OL,14,Fjailed for six weeks for Rashford
OL,15,Fafter England's defeat in the Euro
OL,16,F2020 final in Wembley.
OL,18,FIn January 2021, Rashford was also
OL,19,Fracially abused online after United's
OL,20,F0-0 draw against Arsenal in the
OL,21,FPremier League.
